The following parts were adapted from alt-tab-macos:

- Private API declarations (SLSMainConnectionID, CGSCopyManagedDisplaySpaces,
  CGSCopySpacesForWindows, CGSCopyWindowsWithOptionsAndTags,
  _SLPSSetFrontProcessWithOptions, SLPSPostEventRecordTo,
  _AXUIElementCreateWithRemoteToken, _AXUIElementGetWindow, GetProcessForPID)
  — src/api-wrappers/PrivateApis.swift

- allAXWindows(): combining kAXWindowsAttribute with brute-force
  _AXUIElementCreateWithRemoteToken token iteration to discover windows
  on other Spaces — src/api-wrappers/AXUIElement.swift

- makeKeyWindow(): sending raw WindowServer event bytes via SLPSPostEventRecordTo
  to focus a specific window by CGWindowID
  — originally from https://github.com/Hammerspoon/hammerspoon/issues/370,
  also used in alt-tab-macos src/logic/Window.swift

- Window space mapping via CGSCopyWindowsWithOptionsAndTags per Space
  — src/logic/Spaces.swift
